'''Vishtu''' was a sector of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] after the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] conquered the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] and [[Terraforming/Legends|Vongformed]] it into [[Coruscant/Legends#Yuuzhan'tar|Yuuzhan'tar]]. It was governed by [[Prefect/Legends|Prefect]] [[Ash'ett]] from the [[Vishtu command enclave]].

